RACE.FOOTNOTES: NO QUIT stalked the dueling leaders, moved up on the turn, rallied three wide into the stretch, dueled past the eighth pole, put a head in front near the sixteenth marker and edged away for the win. ITALIAN SYMPHONY raced off the pace between rivals, chased on the turn, rallied four wide into the stretch, closed well inside of DUKE OF GLOUCESTER and got second. DUKE OF GLOUCESTER raced three wide off the pace, chased on the turn, went five wide past the quarter pole, rallied farthest outside in the final furlong and missed for second. CALIBRACHOAMATTERS dueled inside for the lead, dueled on the turn, inched away in upper stretch and dug in gamely to the finish. TATUM dueled two wide for command, dueled on the turn, steadied slightly at the eighth pole and weakened. GABAGOOL broke a step slow, raced off the pace inside, chased on the turn and had no rally.
